OL,3,CJersey consultants told to increase
OL,4,Cprivate work to reduce wait lists
OL,6,FConsultants in Jersey have been
OL,7,Fencouraged to increase their private
OL,8,Fwork to help reduce waiting lists.
OL,10,FAt present, health professionals can
OL,11,Fsplit their time between public and
OL,12,Fprivate patients.
OL,14,FHowever, it was revealed that health
OL,15,Fbosses asked consultants to take on
OL,16,Fmore private clients - a move backed
OL,17,Fby the island's Health Minister.
OL,19,FDeputy Tom Binet said that the aim is
OL,20,Fto bring in money for the healthcare
OL,21,Fservice.
