OL,3,CJersey consultants told to increase
OL,4,Cprivate work to reduce wait lists
OL,6,F"The level of funding that we get
OL,7,Fisn't enough," the minister told ITV
OL,8,FNews. "I know that people are angry
OL,9,Fabout it, not as angry as I am, as
OL,10,Fit's not good to be in this position.
OL,12,F"It's not comfortable for me, and
OL,13,Fwe're going to put it straight, but
OL,14,Fyou cannot sort these things out
OL,15,Fovernight."
