OL,3,CJersey consultants told to increase
OL,4,Cprivate work to reduce wait lists
OL,6,FWhile the Health Minister said the
OL,7,Fmoney brought in by private work will
OL,8,Ffeed into the public service, some
OL,9,Fpublic patients who have already
OL,10,Fwaited years for operations have been
OL,11,Foutraged by the decision.
OL,13,FWith the possibility that those
OL,14,Fwaiting lists could grow longer, some
OL,15,Fpatients have told ITV News they
OL,16,Fbelieve the move is "a scandal".
