OL,3,CJersey consultants told to increase
OL,4,Cprivate work to reduce wait lists
OL,6,FFor context, November's health figures
OL,7,Ffound that while the mean average wait
OL,8,Ftime for all appointments for
OL,9,Felective, non-urgent treatment (such
OL,10,Fas surgeries or specialist visits) is
OL,11,F19 weeks, some are waiting more than a
OL,12,Fyear to be seen.
OL,14,FITV News spoke to one patient who
OL,15,Fdeals with continuous pain, with
OL,16,Fconcerns that a focus on private
OL,17,Fclients could push him further down
OL,18,Fthe waiting list.
