OL,3,CJersey consultants told to increase
OL,4,Cprivate work to reduce wait lists
OL,6,FHowever, Deputy Binet responded that
OL,7,F"in the long run, he won't", adding
OL,8,Fthat work needs to be done as soon as
OL,9,Fpossible to enact "real improvement"
OL,10,Fon waiting times.
OL,12,F"Everybody who pays #6,000 out of
OL,13,Ftheir own pocket - or uses insurance -
OL,14,Fbrings money into the system that
OL,15,Fhelps to shorten the waiting list.
