OL,3,CJersey consultants told to increase
OL,4,Cprivate work to reduce wait lists
OL,6,F"What we need is extra funding, but
OL,7,Fit's a systemic problem; it runs right
OL,8,Fthrough the system. We can't even send
OL,9,Fout appointment reminders to people,
OL,10,Fso there are a lot of things to
OL,11,Faddress.
OL,13,F"If anybody thinks you can address
OL,14,Fthis in five minutes, you can't. If
OL,15,Fsomebody is in real pain, get to their
OL,16,FGP and if necessary write to me, and I
OL,17,Fcan try and get it fast-tracked.
OL,18,FThat's as much as we can do for the
OL,19,Ftime being, but there are no simple
OL,20,Ffixes here.
