OL,3,CJersey consultants told to increase
OL,4,Cprivate work to reduce wait lists
OL,6,FDeputy Binet says he will invite the
OL,7,Fpublic to a meeting in February to
OL,8,Fshed more light on funding proposals
OL,9,Fand to take questions.
OL,11,F"It's a real dilemma, and it's a very
OL,12,Fdifficult time, and it's not one that
OL,13,FI welcome, but it's a reality that
OL,14,Fwe've got to deal with."
